text: "Khatam-al Anbiya (Peace be upon him) Central Headquarter" () is the unified combatant command headquarter of Iranian Armed Forces, under direct command of its General Staff. The strategic headquarter is tasked to plan and coordinate joint military operations within the Iranian forces. As of 2016, its commander is general Gholamali Rashid. == References == Iran Category:Military of Iran
